Notes regarding the GUI:

The Arasan Windows user interface (GUI), the source of which is in the "gui"
directory, is also under this license, and leverages the the lundasvg SVG
rendering package (https://github.com/sammycage/lunasvg), also MIT-licensed.

The SVG piece images (spatial and celtic), which are loaded at runtime, are 
Copyright Maurizio Monge, MIT license.

The chess-openings subdirectory, distributed with the GUI, is a fork
of https://github.com/lichess-org/chess-openings/, and is under the
Creative Commons CC0 1.0 Universal license.
